column2: SELECT top # p.objID, x.SDSSObjid, p.ra, p.dec, p.fuv_mag-p.nuv_mag as fmn, p.fuv_mag, p.nuv_mag FROM photoobjall as p, xSDSSDR7 as x WHERE p.objid = x.objid AND x.distanceRank = # AND x.reverseDistanceRank = #   AND x.reverseMultipleMatchCount = #   AND p.fuv_mag > #   AND p.nuv_mag > #   AND abs(p.fuv_magerr/p.fuv_mag) < #   AND abs(p.nuv_magerr/p.nuv_mag) < #   and p.s2n_nuv > #
